text: Hendrik Johansen (19 April 1889 - 9 June 1948) was a Danish gymnast. He competed in the men's team event at the 1908 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1889 births Category:1948 deaths Category:Danish male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Denmark Category:Gymnasts at the 1908 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Copenhagen
